title: Space Wolves vs Thousand Sons | Warhammer 40k Battle Report

segments.text: [Music]
From the days of the heresy, an ancient
feud has burned.
The Space Wolves,
the sons of Russ, marched to war with
hatred for the Thousand Sons, written
into every saga.
Forged in fury and bound by the oaths of
vengeance, they carry the wrath of Fenis
into battle. Determined to bring ruin to
their most bitter foe. But the thousand
sons stand ready. Cursed by their own
sorcery, yet empowered by the will of
Zech. It is fang against flame, saga
against sorcery. The space wolves face
the thousand sons, and eternal rivals
will clash once more.
